Module com.example.project
Package javafxUI

Class MoneyMarket

java.lang.Object
javafxUI.Account
javafxUI.Savings
javafxUI.MoneyMarket
public class MoneyMarket extends Savings
MoneyMarket class is the extension of Savings class. It contains the data and specific operations needed to handle a Money Market account.
Author:
Sumanth Rajkumar, Shantanu Jain
